&lt;p&gt;We know that the work we do has a high impact on our company&#39;s success and culture. The right person for this position is curious by nature, comfortable in a &quot;take the initiative&quot; environment, loves solving problems, and can thrive in a fast and growing business.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work on live games with millions of active players.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement and test business logic on games and services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform maintenance and updates to keep the game running live.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ship new versions to production, supervise metrics and user feedback after the release.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide timely transparency of development status and risks to interested parties.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will help to solve the most challenging technical issues in the game, partnering with team members to solve them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work in an agile environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
