&lt;li&gt;Plus: you have published apps/games in the mobile app stores.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plus: experience with C++, Objective C, Java for Android, OpenGL, C#, Unity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plus: experience with backend (JavaScript, Node, GoLang, and Kubernetes).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plus: experience being a technical reference for more junior colleagues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;More about you&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
