&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a talented and passionate Senior Game Engineer to join Wildlife’s Marketing Art team in São Paulo, Brazil.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Senior Engineer on the Playables Team, you will not only be responsible for developing playable ads that will attract millions of new users to our games, but also for mentoring junior engineers, leading technical initiatives, and driving improvements to our frameworks and processes.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will play a key role in shaping the technical strategy of our Playables production pipeline, ensuring we deliver high-performance, scalable, and creative interactive ads across multiple platforms.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We know that the work we do has a high impact on our company&#39;s success and culture. The right person for this position is technically excellent, collaborative, proactive, passionate about raising the bar for the entire team and can thrive in a fast and growing business.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop high-quality playable ads that set industry benchmarks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide regular updates on ongoing tasks and inform risks to stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Propose, design and implement reusable frameworks, tools, and systems to improve the efficiency and scalability of Playables production.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide technical guidance and mentorship to junior and mid-level engineers, fostering their growth and ensuring adherence to best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct and encourage rigorous code reviews to maintain a high standard of code quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with Artists, Creative Directors, Product Marketing Specialists, and Data Analysts to align technical solutions with creative and business objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Constantly challenge the status quo and drive innovation within the Playables team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate clearly, respectfully, and effectively, fostering a collaborative and inclusive team environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
