&lt;li&gt;Expertise in JavaScript/TypeScript (web and Node.js ecosystem), HTML, CSS, as well as experience with PixiJS, ThreeJS, and Git.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of shaders and experience with WebGL/WebGI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of game design principles&lt;/li&gt;
