&lt;li&gt;Experience in the game industry &amp;amp; game development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated experience in leading technical initiatives and collaborating with cross-functional teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skills in resource optimization (graphics, sounds, models, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience optimizing performance across different devices&lt;/li&gt;
